---
title: Bengali Salmon & Turmeric Veggies with Coconut Sauce & Toasted Almonds
description: We’ve gone a little bit fancy on you with this snazzy salmon, coated in a creamy coconut sauce and loaded with delicate and aromatic flavours. Accompanied by crunchy broccolini and turmeric-infused veggies, you won't believe you whipped up such a delight.

*Unfortunately, this week's snapper was in short supply, so we've replaced it with salmon. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-bengal-snapper-turmeric-veggies-872feb62.jpg
